---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for Paradigm IT Services."
>
  <main class="bg-surface min-h-screen">
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-on-surface">Terms of Service</h1>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 font-body text-on-surface/80 leading-relaxed">
          <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> May 2026</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Services</h2>
          <p>Paradigm IT Services provides technology consulting, solutions architecture, AI strategy, and managed services. All engagements are governed by a separate Statement of Work (SOW) or service agreement.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>Client deliverables created under a signed agreement are owned by the client upon full payment. Pre-existing frameworks, methodologies, and tools remain the property of Paradigm IT Services.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Confidentiality</h2>
          <p>All information shared during engagements is treated as confidential. We do not disclose client information, projects, or technical details without explicit consent.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Our liability is limited to fees paid for the specific service in question. We are not liable for indirect, consequential, or incidental damages.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by the laws of Jamaica. Any disputes shall be resolved in Jamaican courts.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about these terms? Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@serviceparadigm.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@serviceparadigm.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
